This paper deals with the problem of online prediction learning, which is a core topic in machine learning. The paper focuses on off-policy learning, which is a subfield of reinforcement learning. The paper also discusses the use of function approximation, which is a common technique in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.RO (Robotics).
